WEBVTT

00:03:59.989 --> 00:04:04.087
it doesn't entirely capture
what an emotion is.

00:04:04.592 --> 00:04:07.550
Of course, the physiology
is extremely important,

00:04:07.574 --> 00:04:10.725
but it's not the only reason
why we feel the way we do

00:04:10.749 --> 00:04:12.324
at any given moment.

00:04:14.102 --> 00:04:17.080
What if I was to tell you
that in the 12th century,

00:04:17.104 --> 00:04:20.856
some troubadours didn't see yawning

00:04:20.880 --> 00:04:24.630
as caused by tiredness
or boredom like we do today,

00:04:24.654 --> 00:04:28.008
but thought it a symbol
of the deepest love?

00:04:28.907 --> 00:04:33.146
Or that in that same period,
brave men -- knights --